OL,6,FITV News Deputy Political Editor
OL,7,FAnushka Asthana revealed details of
OL,8,Fthe cuts just over a week ago,
OL,9,Fsparking a fierce backlash from Labour
OL,10,FMPs and causing the government to
OL,11,Frethink some of the measures.
OL,13,FThe move is all part of the
OL,14,Fgovernment's effort to find savings,
OL,15,Fafter global factors and slow economic
OL,16,Fgrowth tightened the Chancellor's
OL,17,Fspending flexibility.
