OL,6,FPip is a benefit designed to help
OL,7,Fpeople with a disability to pay for
OL,8,Fadditional costs, such as wheelchairs,
OL,9,Fcars, above average bills, carers, and
OL,10,Fspecialist equipment.
OL,12,FThe benefit can be claimed by people
OL,13,Fboth in and out of work and is not
OL,14,Fmeans tested. Payments range from
OL,15,F#1,500 and #9,600 a year.
