OL,6,FPeople applying are given points based
OL,7,Fon how much they need support with
OL,8,Feveryday activities, and Kendall
OL,9,Fannounced claimants will now need to
OL,10,Fscore a "minimum of four points in at
OL,11,Fleast one activity to qualify for the
OL,12,Fdaily living element of Pip from
OL,13,FNovember 2026".
OL,15,FThe changes to the thresholds are
OL,16,Fexpected to save the government #5bn.
OL,17,FThe government insists the most
OL,18,Fdisabled people will still be
OL,19,Fprotected.
