OL,6,F"There will always be people who can
OL,7,Fnever work because of the severity of
OL,8,Fdisability or illness", Kendall said.
OL,10,FITV News understands the government
OL,11,Fhad also planned to freeze Pip from
OL,12,Fnext year, but after a backlash from
OL,13,FLabour MPs the plan was scrapped. "I
OL,14,Fcan confirm, we will not freeze Pip",
OL,15,FKendall told the Commons.
OL,17,FThe government is also launching a
OL,18,Freview of the Pip assessment, and has
OL,19,Fannounced an additional #1bn a year
OL,20,Ffor employment support to help people
OL,21,Fget back into work.
