OL,6,FWork capability assessment
OL,8,FKendall also announced the government
OL,9,Fis scrapping the controversial work
OL,10,Fcapability assessment by 2028.
OL,12,FThe move will end a system where
OL,13,Fbenefits payments are linked to
OL,14,Fsomeone's capacity to work, instead
OL,15,FKendall said extra income will be
OL,16,Favailable solely through the Pip
OL,17,Fassessment.
