OL,6,FThe work capability assessment (WCA)
OL,7,Fis currently used to determine who is
OL,8,Feligible for incapacity benefits
OL,9,Fthrough Universal Credit.
OL,11,F"Going through the WCA is complex,
OL,12,Ftime-consuming and often stressful for
OL,13,Fclaimants, especially if they also
OL,14,Fhave to go through the PIP
OL,15,Fassessment", Kendall told MPs.
OL,17,F"More fundamentally, it's based on a
OL,18,Fbinary can, can't work divide when we
OL,19,Fknow the truth is that many people's
OL,20,Fphysical and mental health conditions
OL,21,Ffluctuate."
