OL,6,FConsulting on merging jobseeker's
OL,7,Fallowance (JSA) and employment support
OL,8,Fallowance (ESA)
OL,10,FKendall announced the government will
OL,11,Fconsult on whether to merge
OL,12,Fjobseeker's allowance (JSA) and
OL,13,Femployment support allowance (ESA), a
OL,14,Fmove which would allow people who have
OL,15,Fpaid into the system to get higher
OL,16,Fbenefit payments for a period of time.
