OL,3,CBenefits crackdown announced by
OL,4,Cgovernment in plan to save #5bn by 2030
OL,6,FKendall said it was a "major reform of
OL,7,Fcontributory benefits". The proposal
OL,8,Fwould merge the two benefits into a
OL,9,Ftime-limited unemployment insurance
OL,10,Fwhich is paid at a higher rate.
OL,12,FClaimants would not have to prove they
OL,13,Fare unable to work, in order to
OL,14,Freceive it.
OL,16,FShe said: "So if you have paid into
OL,17,Fthe system, you'll get stronger income
OL,18,Fprotection while we help you get back
OL,19,Fon track."
