OL,6,FIn an effort to encourage more people
OL,7,Fon benefits to look for work, the
OL,8,Fbasic rate of universal credit paid to
OL,9,Fpeople in work or looking for work
OL,10,Fwill be raised, while the rate for
OL,11,Fthose judged unfit for work will be
OL,12,Fcut.
OL,14,FKendall announced there will be "an
OL,15,Fadditional premium for people with
OL,16,Fsevere lifelong conditions, that mean
OL,17,Fthat they will never work, to give
OL,18,Fthem the financial security they
OL,19,Fdeserve".
