OL,6,FThe Work and Pensions Secretary also
OL,7,Fpledged universal credit claimants
OL,8,Fwith severe, lifelong disabilities
OL,9,Fwill face fewer benefits reassessments.
OL,11,F"I can announce for people on
OL,12,Funiversal credit with the most severe
OL,13,Fdisabilities and health conditions
OL,14,Fthat will never improve, we want to
OL,15,Fensure that they are never reassessed
OL,16,Fto give them the confidence and
OL,17,Fdignity they deserve," she told the
OL,18,FCommons.
