OL,6,FThe move was in response to evidence
OL,7,Fshowing many disabled people would
OL,8,Flike to work but are concerned about
OL,9,Fstarting a job in case it doesn't work
OL,10,Fout and they've lost their benefits.
OL,12,FKendall confirmed the move in the
OL,13,FCommon, saying it will give "people
OL,14,Fthe confidence to take the plunge and
OL,15,Ftry work without the fear this will
OL,16,Fput their benefits at risk."
